{"title_page": "You Are the Best Thing", "text_new": "{{distinguish|U R the Best Thing|You're the Best Thing}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = You Are the Best Thing\n| cover      = You-are-the-best-thing-single.jpg\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Ray LaMontagne]]\n| album      = [[Gossip in the Grain]]\n| released   = August 26, 2008\n| format     =\n| recorded   = 2008\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = {{Flat list|\n*[[soul music|Soul]]\n}}\n| length     = 3:51\n| label      = {{Flat list|\n*Stone Dwarf Music, LLC\n*[[RCA Records|RCA]]\n*[[Jive Records|Jive]]\n}}\n| writer     = Ray LaMontagne, Danny Holland\n| producer   = [[Ethan Johns]]\n| prev_title = Three More Days\n| prev_year  = 2007\n| next_title = Meg White\n| next_year  = 2008\n}}\n'''\"You Are the Best Thing\"''' is the [[lead single]] of the album ''[[Gossip in the Grain]]'' by American [[Folk singer|folk]] [[singer-songwriter]] [[Ray LaMontagne]] released on August 26, 2008, by Stone Dwarf Music, LLC, under license to RCA/JIVE Label Group, a unit of Sony Music Entertainment.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/you-are-the-best-thing-single/id288283528 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=November 19, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302065341/http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/you-are-the-best-thing-single/id288283528 |archivedate=March 2, 2012 }}</ref>\n\nThe song hit number five on ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]''{{'s}} [[Adult Alternative Songs]] chart,<ref name=\"bb\"/> and is currently his only single to chart on the [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]], reaching number 90.<ref name=\"bb1\"/>\n\nSinger Jovin Webb sang the song on [[American Idol (season 18)]] during the Showcase Round at [[Aulani]] Resort in [[Kapolei, Hawaii]] which aired on March 29, 2020.\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Chart (2008\u201309)\n! Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" {{singlech